{"about_the_game":"LOOTBAWX let's you collect unique loot by opening <i>free</i> loot boxes. <br><br>You will be awarded a free loot box between every 30 minutes and 2 hours as long as you are playing the game. It is your choice whether to open the crate, sell the crate, or even trade your loot on the marketplace to other fellow LOOTBAWXers!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">REGULAR DROPS</h2>Loot crates dropped every hour and new ones released weekly.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108710/extras/roll.gif?t=1723603837\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">WEAR VALUE, ITEMS GUARANTEED UNIQUE</h2>Loot has WEAR VALUE meaning each item you receive is UNIQUE. NO OTHER CLICKERS HAVE THIS! Each item also has rarity and special effects can be rolled too!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108710/extras/Screenshot_2024-08-13_212737.png?t=1723603837\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">INTERACTABLES</h2>Interactable items such as guns which actually shoot!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108710/extras/interactable.gif?t=1723603837\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">SHOP, BUY AND SELL</h2>Shop where you can SELL your low tier loot for COINS and BUY crates.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108710/extras/shop_screenshot.png?t=1723603837\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">VIRTUAL PLINKO</h2>We even have PLINKO where you can roll to get coins buy even more crates!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108710/extras/plinko.gif?t=1723603837\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Party system!</h2>Join your friends to get loot faster!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108710/extras/party_system_small.png?t=1723603837\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">... And many more features</h2